data.description: Come take a look at Orange town's first certified Energy star home in 2013. 5 Bedrooms and can be a 6th if you use the addt'l loft area on the second floor. Granite countertops in the Kitchen. Open Floor Plan. Fully finished basement can be used as a mother/daughter set up with separate entrance. Two laundry rooms. One on main level the other in the finished basement. Newly painted and sprinkler system in place. Central air throughout. Middle Central air system is 2-3 years old. Roof & A/C is 13 years old. Separate patio for downstairs for privacy. Basketball pad paved in the backyard for recreational purposes. Hardwood floors throughout. HUGE walk up attic 28X48 with 2 windows & electric, can be finished. The master bathroom is gigantic. Has new tub and shower stall and new tile throughout. Close to schools & Pkwy. Do not let this one get away. Bring the whole Family. 2 Minutes away from Blue Ribbon Pearl River schools, public transportation to NYC (via bus & train), & a strip full of shops and eateries.
